  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>INGHAMS OFFERS <a data-udi="umb://document/d137b11ca7414c7b817405b2fd7405b8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d137b11ca7414c7b817405b2fd7405b8}" title="Ski Short Breaks to Switzerland">SHORT SKI BREAKS</a> AND WEEKENDS TO SWITZERLAND FROM £439<br />Book by 17th January 2016 for great savings and first-class rail upgrades</p>
<p><strong>Wednesday 6th January 2016, London</strong> – Ski holiday specialist Inghams is highlighting its weekend and short break holidays to 10 snow-sure ski resorts in Switzerland including <a data-udi="umb://document/1597219bc8c942e685b083f42d203f8f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1597219bc8c942e685b083f42d203f8f}" title="Arosa-Lenzerheide">Arosa</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/a95de5322c984f85bcf0f013c457e8df" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a95de5322c984f85bcf0f013c457e8df}" title="Davos">Davos</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/f6cb1f0178b7447488bbf36b5f109fbc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6cb1f0178b7447488bbf36b5f109fbc}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/b23ef1df250240c5a3657f721fdb96d0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b23ef1df250240c5a3657f721fdb96d0}" title="Klosters">Klosters</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55}" title="St. Moritz">St. Moritz</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50}" title="Saas Fee">Saas Fee</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/7e163ac5c9114f0dae9f3f8d222fa730" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7e163ac5c9114f0dae9f3f8d222fa730}" title="Wengen">Wengen</a> and<a data-udi="umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1}" title="Zermatt"> Zermatt</a>. Booking an Inghams Swiss ski weekend or short break holiday ensures flights, train transfers and accommodation are arranged in advance giving the maximum amount of time on the slopes for guests that only have a few days to spare.</p>
<p>Switzerland is the <strong>only destination featured in Inghams‘ short break</strong> and ski weekend programme due to the <strong>numerous daily flights</strong> from four UK airports, the <strong>modern and scenic Swiss railway services</strong> and <strong>flexible accommodation options</strong>.</p>
<p>All of the Inghams short Swiss ski breaks include return flights from the UK to Zurich or Geneva, free ski carriage when booking with Swiss Airlines, scenic rail transfers and a minimum of three nights’ accommodation. Guests booking <strong>a short break to Switzerland before 17th January will save £25 per person and receive a complimentary 1st class rail upgrade worth £70 per person.</strong></p>
<p>In addition Inghams offers special added-value promotions for certain hotels and resorts such as a complimentary lift pass for all St. Moritz guests, complimentary<strong> daily ski hosting</strong> at selected hotels in Davos and Klosters and complimentary children’s ski school (up to 17 years) at selected hotels in Arosa.</p>
<p>Inghams’ flexible short ski breaks cater to couples looking for a <strong>romantic getaway, new skiers/snowboarders wanting to try a taster weekend, or families and friends up for a spontaneous Swiss escape.</strong> The below packages give a taster of the short breaks holiday options for the current season:</p>
<p><strong>Three nights in Zermatt, Switzerland</strong> – from £543 per person – save £25 per person <br />Zermatt is consistently named as one of the world’s top ski resorts, it boasts a huge ski area at high-altitude, and the breathtaking views of Europe’s most famous peak, the iconic Matterhorn. Inghams is offering three-nights, at the four-star <a data-udi="umb://document/f01376c8cfc8417eafddbd41b11fe366" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f01376c8cfc8417eafddbd41b11fe366}" title="Hotel Rex Garni">Hotel Rex Garni</a> in Zermatt from £543 per person on a bed and breakfast basis, saving £25 per person, departing 3rd April 2016. Price includes return flights from London Heathrow to Zurich and first-class rail transfers. For more information visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk">www.inghams.co.uk</a> or contact 01483 791 114.</p>
<p><strong>Three nights in Arosa, Switzerland</strong> – from £633 per person – save £25 per person <br />Arosa is a long-established ski resort with chocolate box scenery and a fantastic ski area suitable for all abilities. Inghams is offering three-nights at the three-star <a data-udi="umb://document/beec22798fba4443812cbf91d7ee2587" href="/{localLink:umb://document/beec22798fba4443812cbf91d7ee2587}" title="Sorell Hotel Asora">Sorell Hotel </a>Asora from £633 per person on a half-board basis, saving £25 per person, departing 6th March 2016. Price includes return flights from London Heathrow to Geneva and first-class rail transfers. For more information visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk">www.inghams.co.uk</a> or contact 01483 791 114.</p>
<p><strong>Three nights in Saas Fee, Switzerland</strong> – from £643 per person – save £25 per person <br />With an excellent snow record and glacier skiing, Saas-Fee is a beautiful high Alpine village deservedly known as ‘the Pearl of the Alps.’ Inghams is offering three-nights at the four-star <a data-udi="umb://document/551a518c5696430293fe310832569ac7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/551a518c5696430293fe310832569ac7}" title="Hotel Allalin">Hotel Allalin </a>in Saas Fee from £643 per person, saving £25 per person, departing 12th February 2016. Price includes half board accommodation (daily breakfast and six-course evening meal with free daily packed lunch and afternoon pastry buffet), return flights from London Heathrow to Geneva and first-class rail transfers. For more information visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk">www.inghams.co.uk</a> or contact 01483 791 114.</p>
<p><strong>Three nights in Wengen, Switzerland</strong> – from £703 per person – save £25 per person <br />The idyllic village of Wengen lies high up on a sunny, sheltered terrace with spectacular views, dominated by a magnificent trio of peaks – the Eiger (Ogre), Mönch (Monk) and Jungfrau (Maiden). Inghams is offering three-nights, half board at the four-star <a data-udi="umb://document/01c59f0369f647ca9ff14ceaceaa4d30" href="/{localLink:umb://document/01c59f0369f647ca9ff14ceaceaa4d30}" title="Sunstar Alpine Hotel Wengen">Hotel Sunstar Alpine</a> in Wengen from £703 per person, saving £25 per person, departing 12th March 2016. Price includes return flights from London Heathrow to Zurich and first-class rail transfers. For more information visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk">www.inghams.co.uk</a> or contact 01483 791 114.</p>
<p>Inghams offers <strong>daily departures</strong> to Switzerland with scheduled flights available from Heathrow, Manchester, Gatwick and Birmingham.</p>
<p>For more information and Swiss ski holiday packages visit <br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-holiday-types/ski-weekends%20">www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-holiday-types/ski-weekends </a><br />or call 01483 79 11 14</p>
